Name: Description
Commuting by Means of Transportation: The share of individuals who worked in the last week by their usual means of transportation. "Public transit" includes subway, bus, railroad, and ferry; "Carpool, Taxi, Other" includes motorcycle or any other method not listed.

Name: Source Notes
Commuting by Means of Transportation: U.S. Census Bureau, American Community Survey 1-Year Estimates, Table B08006 (2012-2019); retrieved from https://data.census.gov/.
